1. *Beli* slonovi su najveće životinje na planeti. (White elephants are the largest animals on the planet.)

2. *Bela* pustinja je jedna od najzanimljivijih prizora. (The white desert is one of the most interesting sights.)

3. *Beležimo* sve promene u svakodnevnom životu. (We are recording all the changes in everyday life.)

4. *Beležiti* svaki dan je veoma važno. (Recording every day is very important.)

5. *Belina* pokriva većinu površine. (The whiteness covers most of the surface.)

6. *Belom* bojom samo obojiti prozore. (Paint the windows only with white color.)